{"tid":875170,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"#永遠懷念陳百強(離世25周年) - 一生何求 (原唱:陳百強)","createTime":"2018-10-24T17:14:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T17:26:11.000Z","uid":190992,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6e1e9145afd43072362cd7477dabe64925856bed","tid":875170,"uid":190992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T17:14:41.000Z","msg":"謹以此紀念陳百強離世25周年, Danny的一切依然經典.<br />\n<br />\n《一生何求》是Danny於台灣之行中，在一位朋友的車上偶然聽到王傑的《惦記這一些》，覺得它是一首難得之作，結果，Danny回港後將這首歌曲的版權弄到手，亦憑此曲屢獲殊榮，證明了他眼光的獨到。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?list=PLrBzdNpoGVB8HTH0lvlJf3v93XbT0Tgmk&amp;v=qv2_kA6pokk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Flist%3DPLrBzdNpoGVB8HTH0lvlJf3v93XbT0Tgmk%26v%3Dqv2_kA6pokk&d=m29a5ld8Zh9M1evcMgLd2wCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=29e15fa7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?list=PLrBzdNpoGVB8HTH0lvlJf3v93XbT0Tgmk&amp;v=qv2_kA6pokk</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://preview.ibb.co/h2hBmV/smoke_rain_snapshot_2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpreview.ibb.co%2Fh2hBmV%2Fsmoke_rain_snapshot_2.png&h=e1e65d07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#永遠懷念陳百強 - 一生何求 (原唱:陳百強)<br />\n主唱: 夢詞人　原唱: 陳百強<br />\n<br />\n冷暖那可休　回頭多少個秋<br />\n尋遍了卻偏失去　未盼卻在手<br />\n我得到沒有　沒法解釋得失錯漏<br />\n剛剛聽到望到便更改<br />\n不知那裡追究<br />\n<br />\n一生何求　常判決放棄與擁有<br />\n耗盡我這一生　觸不到已跑開<br />\n一生何求　迷惘裡永遠看不透<br />\n沒料到我所失的竟已是我的所有<br />\n<br />\n一生何求　曾妥協也試過苦鬥<br />\n夢內每點繽紛　一消散那可收<br />\n一生何求　誰計較讚美與詛咒<br />\n沒料到我所失的竟已是我的所有<br />\n<br />\n#義不容情,#勁歌金曲,#總選,#一生何求,#陳百強,#新詞,#改編,#粵語歌,#勵志歌,#我的推介,#廣東歌,#歌詞,#音樂,#唱作人,#填詞人,#香港音樂,#創作,#原創音樂,#香港原創,#cantopop,#music,#song,#songs,#popmusic,#hk,#hongkong,#hkmusic,#hongkongmusic"},{"pid":"d518f3b1d0326d762bfb15524589d48b34935c0c","tid":875170,"uid":190992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T11:25:11.000Z","msg":"呢首歌係無線經典電視劇&lt;義不容情&gt;的主題曲, 提提大家&lt;義不容情&gt;下星期會係深夜重播, 好快就可以看到片頭丁有健一路行一路食煙嗰幕..."},{"pid":"f603c3765e55301212848ebe3443c6181ac8e2d8","tid":875170,"uid":77556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T11:43:52.000Z","msg":"練吓唱功先啦， 摙住嗰春袋唱歌咁款"},{"pid":"1038997742703e5880f6c38978394c670aec06c6","tid":875170,"uid":190992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T17:26:11.000Z","msg":"謝謝你的意見. 今次放鬆D唱&quot;一生不可自決&quot;, 請賜教.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?list=PLrBzdNpoGVB8HTH0lvlJf3v93XbT0Tgmk&amp;v=mtAZcvlgYDE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Flist%3DPLrBzdNpoGVB8HTH0lvlJf3v93XbT0Tgmk%26v%3DmtAZcvlgYDE&d=m29a5ld8Zh9M1evcMgLd2wCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=d132d229\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?list=PLrBzdNpoGVB8HTH0lvlJf3v93XbT0Tgmk&amp;v=mtAZcvlgYDE</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://preview.ibb.co/guBaYA/life_cannot_snapshot_3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpreview.ibb.co%2FguBaYA%2Flife_cannot_snapshot_3.png&h=107b131f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}